tr.td: Replaced Seat word; I imported the word from original site's logo. Previously, a white cover created the hole for the A, while now there is no need for it, and the log can be used on a different background color. Furthermore, previously the T was included in the same path of the S drawing, shile now all the word is part of the same path, separated from the S. I slightly moved the and the seat word in order to center them horizontally and align them to the bottom and top of the canvas.
